IN RE APPLICATION FOR PERMIT TO CARRY A HANDGUN OF Mark CHEESEMAN. (Mark P. Cheeseman - Petitioner) C-822 September Term 2018
082155 Supreme Court of New Jersey. MAY 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002412-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
